OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAfter a
OL,6,Fmostly dry start, outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fwill develop later into the evening as
OL,8,Fa weakening band of rain moves
OL,9,Fsoutheastwards across the region.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FCloudy with some light rain
OL,12,For drizzle early morning, especially
OL,13,Fin Kent. Becoming dry with variable
OL,14,Fcloud and bright or sunny spells.
OL,15,FFeeling cooler compared to previous
OL,16,Fdays. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
