OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FUnsettled
OL,6,Fwith an increasing likelihood of wet
OL,7,Fand windy conditions on Friday and
OL,8,Finto the weekend. Drier, brighter and
OL,9,Fwindy on Sunday. Feeling cooler.
